          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1684425153928-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add a small drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> to a pot with a lid over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add <strong>half </strong>the <strong>chopped garlic</strong> (you'll use the rest later!) with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for 1 min or until fragrant</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1684425170922-x200.jpg",
