            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the rice is almost cooked, heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a<strong> </strong>drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, drain, then add your<strong> king prawns </strong>and cook for 4-5 min or until cooked through</p>",
      "order": 6,
