    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>sweet & spicy Korean-style king prawns </strong>with the<strong> garlic rice </strong>and <strong>creamy slaw</strong> to the side</p><p>Sprinkle your <strong>toasted sesame seeds </strong>over the prawns and rice</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
